text: Piet van der Schans (23 June 1934 - 23 April 2003) was a Dutch equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Dutch male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
